<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2634882>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23a–c. Tephritis kovalevi kovalevi: a—tip of aculeus, ventral view; b—aculeus, ventral view; c—spermathecae; df—sonchus cf—palustris and T. kovalevi in natural habitat—d—flower head; e—t—kovalevi kovalevi sitting on the leaf; f— Infested flower head. Scale bar = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2634882/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2634837>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2a–h. Tephritis, spp. wings: a—T. valida; b—T. kogardtauica; c—T. dilacerata dilacerata; d—T. dilacerata kaszabi; e—T. kovalevi kovalevi; f—T. kovalevi kumana; g—T. formosa; h—T. youngiana. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2634837/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2634886>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25a–e. Tephritis kovalevi kumana: a—tip of aculeus, ventral view; b—aculeus, ventral view; c—eversible membrane, ventral view; d—spermathecae; e—glans of phallus, lateral. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
